Package: ledgeR
Type: Package
Title: Utilities for Importing Data from Plaintext Accounting Files
Version: 0.5.3
Author: Trevor L Davis
Maintainer: Trevor L Davis <trevor.l.davis@gmail.com>
URL: https://github.com/trevorld/ledgeR
BugReports: https://github.com/trevorld/ledgeR/issues
Description: Utilities for querying plaintext accounting files from Ledger, HLedger, and Beancount.
Imports:
    dplyr, rlang
Suggests:
    testthat
SystemRequirements: to read ledger files you'll need ledger (>= 3.1),
    to read hledger files you'll need hledger (>= 1.4),
    to read beancount files you'll need beancount (>= 2.0) and hledger (>= 1.4)
